OL,3,CHorse found dead at Appleby horse fair
OL,5,FA horse has died in what's being
OL,6,Fdescribed as potentially 'suspicious
OL,7,Fcircumstances' at Appleby horse fair.
OL,9,FThe piebald gelding is thought to have
OL,10,Fbeen between five and seven years old,
OL,11,Faccording to vets.
OL,13,FAnimal welfare officers, vets, fire
OL,14,Fand rescue officers and police were
OL,15,Fcalled to a grass verge on a road into
OL,16,Fthe village of Brampton from the south
OL,17,Fat 12:40pm on Saturday (6 June).
