OL,3,CHorse found dead at Appleby horse fair
OL,5,FThe piebald gelding, who's
OL,6,Fapproximately 14hh, has distinctive
OL,7,Fmarkings, being mostly white with
OL,8,Fblack patches, all white legs with
OL,9,Ffeathers and a black tail.
OL,11,FA trader's mark sprayed on the horse's
OL,12,Fbody in blue or green paint has been
OL,13,Faltered in an apparent attempt to
OL,14,Fdisguise the trader's identity.
OL,16,FHe was not shod and looks to have been
OL,17,Frecently gelded.
OL,19,FRSPCA Chief Inspector Lyndsey Taylor
OL,20,Fsaid: "This is a very upsetting
OL,21,Fincident.
OL,26,@|D@GOU
