OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1781028675
OL,3,CHorse found dead at Appleby horse fair
OL,5,F"At the moment we don't know the cause
OL,6,Fof this horse's death, but it seems as
OL,7,Fthough he may have died in suspicious
OL,8,Fcircumstances.
OL,10,F"We are looking for evidence of him
OL,11,Fbeing worked, handled or traded and
OL,12,Fwant to hear from the person
OL,13,Fresponsible for him, or anyone who can
OL,14,Fhelp us to identify them."
